{"tid":363212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立會垃圾桶火警案　楊振權拒楊逸朗保釋申請：兩年刑期恰當","createTime":"2017-08-17T13:17:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T02:34:16.000Z","uid":34410,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a4dd754e1cdab253e85592f8c39a1879ed1ff144","tid":363212,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T13:17:09.000Z","msg":"【立會垃圾桶火警案　官拒楊逸朗保釋申請：兩年刑期恰當 | 本土新聞】<br />\n<br />\n立法會前年十二月審議俗稱「網絡廿三條」的《版權（修訂）條例草案》，當晚立法會示威區一個垃圾桶起火。前樹仁大學學生會會長楊逸朗經審訊，被裁定串謀縱火罪成，判監兩年。楊就定罪及刑期提上訴，高等法院今日（十六日）處理其保釋申請，被副庭長楊振權駁回，並認為兩年的判刑恰當，又指其上訴無合理和成功機會。不少市民到庭聽審支持楊，坐滿旁聽席，散庭時楊向旁聽席表示：「唔駛擔心我！」（節錄）<br />\n<br />\n上訴庭係唔係淨係得依幾個官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲信法治個d真係on 9 <br />\n<br />\n唔知仲有冇連登仔記得joe yeung <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c7f01bad64c597b9284dfccc7d1f49789e1d3d","tid":363212,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T13:17:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d77a94d17e63d40bb5cef9261071a82203001cc6","tid":363212,"uid":38795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T13:19:51.000Z","msg":"香港法治先鋒楊振權法官，絕對係一個好官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲好過杜浩成法官，陳碧橋法官<br />\n將中國依法治國既思維帶入香港，完全聽從國家領導人來港既呼籲，確保香港社會繁榮穩定和諧，功不可抹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎緊七警都係佢，等睇放生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75bf597e8a7cb1f08d7315749dbb51d804fdc861","tid":363212,"uid":38795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T14:51:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/17/223843_38b43d1601b9701879f5fc3fc383bc